Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep in here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a hotel, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the content and sign here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me catch you in here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you passed out drunk \N in a back alley like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thankful that you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked if you had any cigarettes on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoking is not permitted inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go outside and smoke all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:33.87,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,171)\pos(366,315)}Eva's Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you put my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only bag you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had another shoulder bag with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a thief probably stole it while \N you were passed out in the alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had something really important in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you want to fill out a stolen property report?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although personally, I think it would be a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your key?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My whole bag was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and open my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone broke in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll have to change the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Ms. Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been asking since yesterday, but about the room bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the advance payment I got ran out a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't receive payment for the overdue days, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my suitcase was broken into...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need payment for the overdue \N days and a replacement key.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want money, I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to leave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was some bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that is why you came to me for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were the one who left \N saying we would never see each other again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen each other in a while, so \N why don't you at least buy me a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you are out of money just \N because someone stole your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never come across another woman \N who spent her money as freely as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No amount of money would have ever been enough for you, the way you spent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were out of money anyway, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much will you pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking how much you'll pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of man would pay for a woman \N he has slept with so many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go stand out in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some curious weirdo might buy a drink for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even an alcoholic hag like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure you didn't leave it at my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you didn't leave it at the next store you went to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything after this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you had something important in there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if it had any real value, you should forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you could get money for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to the pub over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they said you had wandered off this way, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had such a good time drinking \N together last night, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drank... with you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean I'll have to reintroduce myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about getting some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hotel room was vandalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't seem like you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even open your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel room key is still in here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had returned your bag sooner, you wouldn't \N have been chased out of your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I'm grateful you came to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because I'm grateful to that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you left the pub last night, you forgot your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would never see you again, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thanks to that bag, we are here, together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must have been something very important in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all I have left in my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo album?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fine man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall correctly, he was the director of a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I tell you that last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and that you respected him very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said he passed away ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had such a sad expression when \N you talked about it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was your fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even told you about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe his name was Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't forget him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I say last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should forget about him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only page that doesn't have any pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There used to be some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some traces remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took them out because I had no need for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go drinking with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you used to run a security firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in southern France, Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the longtime client I was guarding was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I shut the company down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've both had it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is important is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to enjoy the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Al Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like this song, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not very good at dancing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands around my waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this song, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was another guy who wasn't very good at dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you always stayed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want another drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hold your liquor, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... wanna go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, there is something I have to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pictures you took from the album.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hide them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the pictures, and I'll tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are looking for Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you didn't burn those pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know where Tenma is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pictures you are talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ones with that boy in them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has grown up into a pretty boy with blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him in Düsseldorf about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get you back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.80,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(329,0)\pos(346,306)}Düsseldorf \N Spring 1995
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot of rumors, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as those rumors say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been married three times and I have been divorced three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my father's will and the condolence money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm living luxuriantly, lacking nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Dr. Becker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same old story for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in with the management, so \N no chance of promotion for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in Tenma's case, he's now \N the head of the surgical department.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And rumor has it that he will become the director someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about being left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, my life isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is not about being promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way do I want to end up like Tenma, \N who has no time for women or fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma still hasn't gotten married?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've introduced him to tons of women, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he puts work first and isn't really interested in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I set him up with someone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the daughter of the state legislator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she is really fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't get his attention, I'm giving up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you call me, Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the daughter of the former hospital director, you've \N never even glanced in my direction before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have imagined that you would \N ask me to spend some time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you say you don't lack anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you are actually pretty lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you will let me, I'll lend you my ear any time you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That state legislator's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let her meet Kenzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you still haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better make it tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through a lot of trouble to set this up just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't know until I meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the clock that Mr. Junkers \N from the hospital was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the clock in the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your date!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a beautiful wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My watch is only an accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't bother looking at the time anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why it feels like time is moving faster and faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Ms. Angelika, the daughter of \N State Legislator Berger, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that the world revolves around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think there is nothing in this \N world that you can't get, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a mole on my inner thigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kisses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always kisses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kenzou Tenma, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went home, all because you were shopping \N at that place and got here late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something bad to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you apologize to her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give her a call right now, I'm sure she will forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to swing by the hospital for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you cut it out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Johan, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.53,0:22:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she saw Johan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll kill her after all.
